        <description>An artificial nose developed by DAON for culinary assistance. Its highly sensitive sense of smell detects and removes problematic ingredients, slightly increasing cooking time but greatly reducing the risk of food poisoning in the finished dish. Favored by high-end hotel chefs who willingly sacrifice speed in pursuit of hygiene and quality.</description>
